Package au.gov.sbr.core.client.beans

Interface Summary
PasswordCallback This class has the sole purpose of relaying back the key store password.
 

Class Summary
AttachmentBean This bean represents an Attachment and Attachment instances on the Standard Business Document Message.
BeanBase Represents the base definition to encapsulate many objects into the single object bean.
BusinessDocumentBean This bean represents a Business Document and Business Document instances on the Standard Business Document Message.
ClientBean This bean represents the client application's main window and all the properties that are exposed to the GUI for binding.
CredentialBean This bean represents the data in a AbrUserCredential object from the ABR KeyStore API.
KeyStoreBean This bean represents the Authentication KeyStore.
ResponseBean This bean represents the request/response pair.
SOAPFaultBean This bean class represents the SOAP Fault / SBR Core Exception pair that may have been raised during communications with SBR Core Services.
 

Exception Summary
AuthenticationException This class and its subclasses are a form of Throwable that indicates conditions that this application might want to catch
